# Story Styles
msgid ""
"Plain narration: Restrained language, minimal embellishment, recording like "
"a bystander."
msgstr ""
"Narration sobre : langage retenu, ornements minimes, relatant les faits "
"comme un simple témoin."

msgid ""
"Poetic lyricism: Short sentences and parallelism, sparse use of allusions, "
"avoiding flowery language."
msgstr ""
"Lyrisme poétique : phrases courtes et parallélismes, usage parcimonieux des "
"allusions, en évitant le langage ampoulé."

msgid ""
"Taoist nature: Tinted with Taoist vocabulary, not obscure, focusing on a "
"single thought."
msgstr ""
"Nature taoïste : teintée de vocabulaire taoïste, sans être obscure, centrée "
"sur une seule pensée."
